commit.message:
Allow multi-vol ENDARC where NEXTVOL flag is missing.

Let SPLIT_AFTER on last file to trigger next volume.

Fixes: #97

Check unrar tool with -? parameter

The semantics of the check are the same but this will
fit unrar-free when it is installed as unrar.

doc: add breaking change note to v3.2 release notes

Fixes: #70

ci: use proper unrar

Seems mingw unrar is too friendly with / separator.

test: skip unicode.rar

It contains untagged unicode, which means extracting
works only if systems is already utf8 mode.

Need to replace it with better test file.
Use OS separator to access filename
test: run unrar also with forced tool setting

Silence CRC check during seeking

Fixes: #73

Reposition DirectReader before each read

Otherwise parallel reads from different opened files
on RarFile that is backed by file object can confuse
each other.

Closes: #81
test: read vols with forced tool use

Cleanup check-psw, change api

It may be useful to run it on file entries too.
